[normal] illustrated this phenomenon in a TV programme shown in the Autumn of 2009, when he was interviewed with Professor McKitrich.  The programme presented a scene of part of the Amazon which had suffered an unusual drought in 2005, and asked the two men whether this was due to ACW.  Shooting immediately from the lip Watson said “yes”.  Yet he had no basis for his view, which was mere PR for the IPCC’s unsubstantiated storyline.  McKitrich sensibly said he knew nothing about the facts and could not comment – and showed up Watson.
